21 7. AN OPERATOR ASSERTING THE OPERATOR’S LEGAL
22 RIGHTS, WHETHER IN COURT OR THROUGH PROCEDURES PROVIDED BY ANY LOCAL,
23 STATE, OR FEDERAL AGENCY; OR
24 8. EXCEPT IN THE CASE OF EGREGIOUS MISCONDUCT OR
25 WHERE DEACTIVATION IS OTHERWISE REQUIRED BY LAW, THE RESULTS OF A
